Puppet module: monit

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages monit software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include monit              # Install and run monit with standard configurations.
include monit::disable     # Disable monit service.
include monit::disableboot # Disable monit service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include monit::absent      # Remove monit package.

DEPENDENCIES:
